{"tid":589942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天眼直擊】元朗村屋燈火通明　慣匪照闖　掠20萬財物　利市照偷","createTime":"2018-03-12T08:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T11:07:51.000Z","uid":10958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5c90ed4bf1936da88b65772291086cfc0020008e","tid":589942,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>【天眼直擊】元朗村屋燈火通明　慣匪照闖　掠20萬財物　利市照偷</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266477/xlarge/4e2498394ca246ff0a826d2d2707cb7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266477%2Fxlarge%2F4e2498394ca246ff0a826d2d2707cb7e.jpg&h=7ef0bbe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">疑犯戴帽及口罩。(CCTV片段截圖)</span><br />\n<br />\n元朗屏山出現猖獗獨行爆竊匪！一名戴帽及口罩的獨行慣匪，昨凌晨爬後巷水渠，經天台闖入蝦尾新村一間燈火通明的三層高村屋。他躡手躡腳開門入房，不顧房內有人睡覺，擸走戶主的手機及嫁妝。然後在客飯廳東翻西摷，連小朋友的書包也不放過，偷走金擺設、手機及利市。犯案過程被閉路電視拍下，住戶貼街招及在網上發布疑犯照片緝兇，並希望市民提高警覺。住戶接受香港01訪問時，直斥竊匪猖狂，希望將事件「一傳十十傳百，大家知多啲呢個犯人資料，等警方盡快可以緝捕佢。」<br />\n<br />\n犯案過程﹕<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266490/xlarge/11931d2d9136a371912723d81123cfd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266490%2Fxlarge%2F11931d2d9136a371912723d81123cfd1.jpg&h=94cf587b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266489/xlarge/87ef53008ab158bf282ad2de0e7d5e94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266489%2Fxlarge%2F87ef53008ab158bf282ad2de0e7d5e94.jpg&h=88e77bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266488/xlarge/717ad42a8f7d28a1639e63143b427da1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266488%2Fxlarge%2F717ad42a8f7d28a1639e63143b427da1.jpg&h=f323a175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266492/xlarge/39a467944de6e26cc0250d05ea3d355f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266492%2Fxlarge%2F39a467944de6e26cc0250d05ea3d355f.jpg&h=708cda7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266493/xlarge/e5a209422fc6e810cd236de9aae307de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266493%2Fxlarge%2Fe5a209422fc6e810cd236de9aae307de.jpg&h=ab7b1b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266494/xlarge/7df4bffda774ef2950c53a0036626051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266494%2Fxlarge%2F7df4bffda774ef2950c53a0036626051.jpg&h=434f4211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266491/xlarge/dd160461b22ea7c428a34d8449bf3337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266491%2Fxlarge%2Fdd160461b22ea7c428a34d8449bf3337.jpg&h=89b62747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一家七口在屋內　竊匪照搜掠<br />\n<br />\n據涉案村屋的住戶陳太指出，他們一家人居於上址一棟三層高連天台的村屋，昨凌晨約1時許，5名成人及2名小童已入睡，全屋睡房皆有人，但未有關上客飯廳的燈。當晚刮大風，風聲甚大，他們未聽到屋內有其他異響。約2小時後，其中一名家人因感背部「涼浸浸」而驚醒，才發現房門被打開，手機不翼而飛，手袋被移至房門外，懷疑有人入屋爆竊，於是報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n住戶損失20多萬元嫁妝及財物<br />\n<br />\n警方在凌晨3時許接獲一名姓陳43歲女子報案，指她睡醒後發現手機不見了，其手袋被移至走廊，裡面的財物被偷走。警方到場調查，經初步點算後，證實總值約20多萬元的金器、手飾及手錶等被盜去。案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266467/xlarge/819cd5782300e75d713e19a2eabfc548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266467%2Fxlarge%2F819cd5782300e75d713e19a2eabfc548.jpg&h=cde34cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">放在門外旁的金擺設被偷走，只留下膠盒。（余睿菁攝）</span><br />\n<br />\nCCTV直擊犯案過程　疑犯躡手躡腳搜掠<br />\n<br />\n戶主陳太指，他們事後與警方翻看客廳閉路電視片段，發現在凌晨2時10分起6分鐘內，一名身材矮小的中國籍男子，戴著鴨舌帽、口罩、手套，身穿黑色長袖上衣、牛仔褲及波鞋，背上孭有一個黑色袋。他放輕腳步在客飯廳內搜掠，翻找所有儲物櫃，甚至連飯檯上小孩子的書包都一一搜掠。陳太指，除了偷去家人的嫁妝及飾物，亦掠走客廳的利市、一個金製擺件、一部正在充電的iPhone6S及一部已損壞的舊手機。<br />\n<br />\n犯人疑攀水渠上天台入屋<br />\n<br />\n由於閉路電視對正村屋大門，他們相信竊匪是經村屋後巷攀水渠而上，由天台入屋。陳太指，即使家中燈火通明，每個房間皆有人睡覺，賊人仍敢犯案，直斥犯人猖狂﹕「個賊好大膽，係度出入咁耐。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266468/xlarge/5d7fbab8e8c0106b6e34fbcd32ec2057.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266468%2Fxlarge%2F5d7fbab8e8c0106b6e34fbcd32ec2057.jpg&h=6d366c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">賊人偷走一部手機，但未有拿走手提電腦。（余睿菁攝）</span><br />\n<br />\n疑犯曾爆竊一間餐廳，亦被CCTV拍下。(網上圖片)<br />\n賊人曾被撞破　亮刀求放人<br />\n<br />\n另一住戶鄧先生表示，他事後知悉此賊人是慣匪，去年主要在廈村出沒，涉及數宗案件，常在凌晨時段犯案，不怕家中有人，「好猖狂架，全屋開晒燈都照入屋。」去年年底，有村民目擊賊人潛入屋內，立即喝止，賊人遂亮出利器，以廣東話稱﹕「我走架啦，放我走啦！」然後逃之夭夭；亦有另一間餐廳遇竊後，CCTV拍攝犯人樣貌，與是次案件的疑犯脗合。<br />\n<br />\n廣傳犯人長相　盼村民提高警覺<br />\n<br />\n鄧又指，蝦尾新村向來治安良好，是次屬近年首宗爆竊案件。他家中本來有飼養狗隻，惟近日已離世，會考慮加裝更多閉路電視及再養狗隻防盜。他們托友人在社交網站分享事件，亦在元朗區張貼賊人相貌，希望眾人提高警覺，「係圍村內一傳十十傳百，大家知多啲呢個犯人資料，等警方盡快可以緝捕佢。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266476/xlarge/8ca4e3321362a284512eb74b8fcfdc01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266476%2Fxlarge%2F8ca4e3321362a284512eb74b8fcfdc01.jpg&h=35a78f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">疑犯曾爆竊一間餐廳，亦被CCTV拍下。(網上圖片)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1266471/xlarge/da276730160b1fd859839f8506b98f6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1266471%2Fxlarge%2Fda276730160b1fd859839f8506b98f6f.jpg&h=1d00be0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">拍攝犯案過程的CCTV。(余睿菁攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/166959/-%E5%A4%A9%E7%9C%BC%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9D%91%E5%B1%8B%E7%87%88%E7%81%AB%E9%80%9A%E6%98%8E-%E6%85%A3%E5%8C%AA%E7%85%A7%E9%97%96-%E6%8E%A020%E8%90%AC%E8%B2%A1%E7%89%A9-%E5%88%A9%E5%B8%82%E7%85%A7%E5%81%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F166959%2F-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%25B1%258B%25E7%2587%2588%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%2580%259A%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%2585%25A3%25E5%258C%25AA%25E7%2585%25A7%25E9%2597%2596-%25E6%258E%25A020%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%2585%25A7%25E5%2581%25B7&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ6649%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=06f5e42a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/166959/-%E5%A4%A9%E7%9C%BC%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9D%91%E5%B1%8B%E7%87%88%E7%81%AB%E9%80%9A%E6%98%8E-%E6%85%A3%E5%8C%AA%E7%85%A7%E9%97%96-%E6%8E%A020%E8%90%AC%E8%B2%A1%E7%89%A9-%E5%88%A9%E5%B8%82%E7%85%A7%E5%81%B7</a>"},{"pid":"90ff6196051b6a5d308d8a608792960103eca8d7","tid":589942,"uid":44333,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"ｌｅｎｏｖｏ狗也不屌"},{"pid":"4a692a3513c7c5c3e16202267ceba2ddef2a63a7","tid":589942,"uid":5650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"條友放迷煙呀？ 七個人都感覺唔到有人爆格<br />\n仲要開哂燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cb69ad19d235a1c7442e716019ac1af48003e6","tid":589942,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90ff6196051b6a5d308d8a608792960103eca8d7","tid":589942,"uid":44333,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"ｌｅｎｏｖｏ狗也不屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:02:15.000Z","msg":"賊都唔想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc7773ec2ab902dfba627b1f982c7498015ba0a","tid":589942,"uid":80966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}